                "<p style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:\'-apple-system\'; font-size:16px; color:#24292e; background-color:#ffffff;\">　　(2)第二趟排序：在待排序的arr[2],arr[3].....arr[n]中选出最小的元素与arr[2]进行交换；</span></p>\n"
                "<p style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:\'-apple-system\'; font-size:16px; color:#24292e; background-color:#ffffff;\">　　。。。。。。。</span></p>\n"
